{"about_the_game":"Hired by a mysterious trillionaire in the not so distant future, Eevi keeps trespassers out and fights the varmints. This mall is a time capsule from a different era. The rich have taken to the skies and abandoned the frozen surface. Gazing at the suffering below from the luxury of their own miniature Earths. Stranded on the deserted island the mall sits on, Eevi the wage slave is left to explore this trillionaire's forgotten playground.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771550/extras/dropkick.gif?t=1731723112\" /><br><br>Fight the monsters of the mall in thirdperson. Manage a small inventory to traverse different sectors of the mall and survive their various monster encounters. Take a dive into this mall\u2019s shifting corridors. The Red Silhouette haunts these walls. Appearing to Eevi as warnings. These calls from distant memories open the door for her to explore the mall\u2019s many non-euclidean passages. Experiencing what the mall remembers about us, Eevi is whirlpooled into our cycle of violence.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771550/extras/ezgif-6-32eb0eb4af.gif?t=1731723112\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hey!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2771550/917f76e0030099bcd137cb808343c0197dc5a172.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2771550/f27913085c22c599a3fe2bd65563089fe2e89f36.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2771550/4fb8d8c3c5e33a1e8a3646d8bd95ce591cffed33.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2771550/4eac224f4346704cc1bc712ab9243374671503ef.jpg"},{"name":"The End","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2771550/28509